Then answer this question.

5
00:00:13,960 --> 00:00:17,120
When do the children do their homework?

6
00:00:19,320 --> 00:00:22,699
The Sawyers live at 87 King Street.

7
00:00:22,800 --> 00:00:30,019
In the morning, Mr Sawyer goes to work and the children go to school.

8
00:00:30,699 --> 00:00:34,140
Their father takes them to school every day.

9
00:00:35,420 --> 00:00:38,219
Mrs Sawyer stays at home every day.

10
00:00:38,840 --> 00:00:40,759
She does the housework.

11
00:00:41,320 --> 00:00:44,659
She always eats her lunch at noon.

12
00:00:45,939 --> 00:00:50,079
In the afternoon, she usually sees her friends.

13
00:00:50,179 --> 00:00:53,500
They often drink tea together.

14
00:00:54,679 --> 00:00:58,259
In the evening, the children come home from school.

15
00:00:59,000 --> 00:01:01,019
They arrive home early.

16
00:01:02,600 --> 00:01:05,179
Mr Sawyer comes home from work.

17
00:01:05,740 --> 00:01:07,640
He arrives home late.

18
00:01:08,820 --> 00:01:13,379
At night, the children always do their homework.

19
00:01:14,000 --> 00:01:15,100
Then they go to bed.

20
00:01:15,200 --> 00:01:20,239
Mr Sawyer usually reads his newspaper.

21
00:01:20,840 --> 00:01:24,679
But sometimes, he and his wife watch television.

